CGCC's brand identity is a beautiful combination of serenity and fellowship. And while proudly displayed within the logo, it was deemed missing from their web presence. Seeing the potential there, I worked towards a solution to help create a welcoming atmosphere.

To start, CGCC's color spectrumâranging from hot to cold tonesâtallies upwards of seven with six used in their logo alone. To <strong>emphasize the feeling of serenity and provide a purpose to each color</strong>, I opted to have cooler tones act as the primary hues. Following tones, such as red and yellow, were utilized to prioritize the significance of specified elements, and the greys and dark blue brought support to the content.

