The leaders of The Oniru Group always focused on empowering people to perform better. And now that they're business was finally up and running, it was time to return the favor.

The first step was getting people familiar with them. The steps I tookâ<strong>stating the value proposition in the form of call-to-actions, benefits, and features, creating persona-focused design and copy, minimizing the navigation to its essentials and linking to the most sought after content</strong>âwere all inspired by the anatomy of a great homepage. <strong>Narrowing down their color scheme from seven shades of blue to three</strong> contrasted elements better against one another and became simpler for users to coordinate with. And, the <strong>white space established a sense of an open environment</strong> where users can feel comfortable.";}i:244;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"229";s:8:"meta_key";s:16:"_section_1_blurb";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5efd211f1626a";}i:245;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:39:"section_2_images_w_caption_show_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:1:"0";}i:246;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:40:"_section_2_images_w_caption_show_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5f1235c8ed299";}i:247;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:34:"section_2_images_w_caption_gallery";s:10:"meta_value";s:89:"a:6:{i:0;s:2:"52";i:1;s:3:"215";i:2;s:3:"217";i:3;s:3:"341";i:4;s:3:"342";i:5;s:3:"343";}";}i:248;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:35:"_section_2_images_w_caption_gallery";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5efd33e259ccf";}i:249;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:26:"section_2_images_w_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:0:"";}i:250;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:27:"_section_2_images_w_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5efd33d559cce";}i:251;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:15:"section_3_blurb";s:10:"meta_value";s:1175:"<h2>Rebranded as an Expert</h2>
When it comes to healthcare, users are often quick to Google their questions. The results predetermine a provider's level of expertise to the user. The content on CGCC's previous website failed to target user queries causing search engines not to recognize them as an expert. The team and I made it our mission to correct this.

We started by infixing questions into section headers resembling what users may search for. Next, we examined their current audience and found that roughly <strong>90% arrive as patient referrals from primary care physicians</strong>. Because they've already transitioned into becoming a patient, it would be counter-intuitive to target this audience. So instead, we opted for the remainderâ<strong>users looking for a second opinion</strong>. Because of this, we dedicated <strong>pages describing in detail what a second opinion is, how it works, and what a user can do to get one</strong>. Call-to-actions, highlighted of cardinal significance, were incorporated throughout the site encouraging more traffic to those pages. It also stands as one of the premier interactions above the fold on the home page.";}i:252;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:16:"_section_3_blurb";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5efd211f1626a";}i:253;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:39:"section_4_images_w_caption_show_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:1:"0";}i:254;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:40:"_section_4_images_w_caption_show_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5f1235c8ed299";}i:255;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:34:"section_4_images_w_caption_gallery";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"a:1:{i:0;s:2:"52";}";}i:256;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:35:"_section_4_images_w_caption_gallery";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5efd33e259ccf";}i:257;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:26:"section_4_images_w_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:0:"";}i:258;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:27:"_section_4_images_w_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:19:"field_5efd33d559cce";}i:259;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8:"meta_key";s:39:"section_5_images_w_caption_show_caption";s:10:"meta_value";s:1:"0";}i:260;O:8:"stdClass":3:{s:7:"post_id";s:3:"226";s:8: